attributes.mlflow.spanInputs:
{"database_schema": ""Description for table: SignalTransaction"
type SignalTransaction implements Transaction @entity {
  "Unique identifier for the transaction"
  id: ID!
  "Block number in which the transaction was included"
  blockNumber: Int!
  "Timestamp of when the transaction occurred"
  timestamp: Int!
  "Account that signed the transaction"
  signer: GraphAccount!
  "Type of the transaction"
  type: TransactionType!
  "Amount of signal involved in the transaction"
  signal: BigInt!
  "Number of tokens involved in the transaction"
  tokens: BigInt!
  "Associated subgraph deployment"
  subgraphDeployment: SubgraphDeployment!
  "Fees deducted during withdrawal"
  withdrawalFees: BigInt!
}"}
